```plantuml
@startuml spikecodes_stotra

actor User
participant "AWS Amplify" as Amplify
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Node.js/Express Backend" as Backend
participant "MongoDB Atlas" as MongoDB
participant "External APIs" as ExternalAPIs

User -> Amplify: Accesses application
Amplify -> Frontend: Serves static assets
Frontend -> Backend: API request (with JWT)
Backend -> MongoDB: Query user data
MongoDB --> Backend: Returns user data
Backend -> ExternalAPIs: Fetch stock data
ExternalAPIs --> Backend: Returns stock data
Backend --> Frontend: Returns API response
Frontend -> User: Renders updated UI

@enduml
```